Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.85,0:02:34.93,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)}It is currently the Great Age of Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.93,0:02:36.48,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}A struggle between countless pirates began
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:40.06,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}while looking for the great treasure, One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.06,0:02:42.65,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}left behind by the legendary Pirate King, Gold Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:46.65,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}The boy who became a rubber man after eating the Gomu Gomu Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.65,0:02:48.57,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}Monkey D. Luffy, is one of the many adventurers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:50.99,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}who went out to sea to become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.45,0:02:55.45,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Luffy and his companions have already experienced countless adventures.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:03:00.33,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}Not even the World Government can ignore their existence any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.42,0:03:03.21,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:06.80,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What adventure is waiting for us next?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.09,0:03:10.26,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,0)}Today, the crew aiming for the New World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.26,0:03:13.60,Gold,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(0,200)}will continue through the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:25.45,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace in the great war against the Navy, Luffy was struck by despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.45,0:03:28.68,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate King?!  Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:30.35,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.89,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}weak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.97,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was reminded how much his friends mean to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:43.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And then, at the Dark King Rayleigh's suggestion, he returned to Marineford.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.57,0:03:50.64,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Crew, scattered across the world, received a message hidden in Luffy's baffling actions. { def: shortened to fit. }
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.72,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,They now are acting on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:59.50,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy says he's gonna be the Pirate King... {Disclaimer: Once again, please double-check any lines from 514 up against the currently-non-existent edited and QCed script to maintain consistency.}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:03.46,Main,Nami,0000,0000,0000,,so I can't take my job as a navigator lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.55,Thoughts,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:09.70,Thoughts,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,The Sunny hasn't showed its full potential yet! { def: remove "still" from 513's line }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.05,0:04:13.56,Thoughts,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,The only captain who can make\Nthe Sunny into my dream ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.20,0:04:16.60,Thoughts,Franky,0000,0000,0000,,is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.80,0:04:23.91,Thoughts,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, the next time we meet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.18,Thoughts,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:31.12,Thoughts,Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,support you as the greatest cook in the world, so that you may become the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:47.20,Narrator TOP,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is Sword Mountain Island on the Grand Line,\NTeena Gaina Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.60,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in and have a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:56.14,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge crowd!  What is everyone looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.78,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like they've captured some strange creature.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.78,0:05:05.07,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Now gather around and behold this bizarre life form!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.78,0:05:07.03,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,No chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.50,0:05:08.95,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,No flesh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:10.91,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,No eyeballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.87,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,This creature has the appearance of a real skeleton!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:21.88,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, his arms only have a single joint!\NIs there a more extraordinary creature anywhere?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.22,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Don't try to deceive us\Nwith cheap tricks, charlatans!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.32,0:05:28.51,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What?  Are you not satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:32.14,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,That thing hasn't moved a muscle yet! { def: he is a skeleton and doesn't have any muscels.  yohohohoho! }
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.40,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a mannequin, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.35,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san has made his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.35,0:05:42.90,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,In which case, I must also do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:45.65,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, skeleton!  Quit messing with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.65,0:05:48.59,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot just sit here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.06,0:05:52.71,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you understand?  That's right, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.71,0:05:54.45,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,This wouldn't be much of a show otherwise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:57.32,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,How may I be of aid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:00.22,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Just moving around would be plenty helpful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:01.94,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,So move!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:03.50,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:15.47,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,You were not the least bit scared when you saw me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:20.98,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,and what's more, you invited me to join your crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:23.90,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you! {Copy-paste from 405}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.88,0:06:26.36,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Join my crew! {End copy-paste from 405}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:28.49,Flashbacks,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?  Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:34.45,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,It had been fifty years.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:40.15,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Could you imagine my joy, after drifting around on the dark ocean for so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.90,0:06:46.38,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,A certain man stole my shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:51.89,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?!\NIf you need a shadow, I'll get it back for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.29,0:07:20.54,Flashbacks,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I am glad to be alive! {More copy-paste from 405. Just this one line.}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:24.98,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:28.14,Flashbacks,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,May I join your crew?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.14,0:07:29.52,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, fine by me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:31.76,Flashbacks,Usopp & Sanji,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}He joined...{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.76,0:07:33.59,Flashbacks,Chopper & Franky,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Just like that?!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:40.81,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how brilliantly you were shining to me? {Can't seem to think of a way to phrase this that sounds natural... Or not gay.}{ def: i wouldn't dream of touching this line. }
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.27,0:07:48.11,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty years of praying for a miracle, answered at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.11,0:07:49.41,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back my money!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:50.57,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:55.62,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!  I thought we'd make some money off this,\Nbut it looks hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:58.05,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,If he won't do as he's told, we'll just have to force{\fscx250}-{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:58.98,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.43,0:08:03.96,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.10,0:08:11.32,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Forty degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:15.14,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}Huh?!{\i1}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.14,0:08:17.39,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, it's so difficult!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:20.04,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,He's really talking and moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.25,Main,Womany McLady,0000,0000,0000,,How creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.81,Main,Womany McLady,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that creature?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:27.82,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,If I try going below forty-five degrees,\NI end up slipping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:30.71,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,However, once I can master this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.85,0:08:35.76,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,I may be of more use to Luffy-san. {Sure. You can become more helpful by learning to lean against a wall at a specific angle without falling over. BEST. ABILITY. EVER.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:39.79,Thoughts,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought,\Nperhaps I should consider another method?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.71,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,He's holding a guitar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.71,0:08:47.84,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What is he gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.07,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning now?! {Now, who can spot the silly animation-mistake in this shot? xD}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.07,0:08:53.67,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to put on a crappy show!\NThis is just an exhibition!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.67,0:08:58.00,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,An exhibition is fine with me!  Call it whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:02.10,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,The word "Loneliness" no longer exists in my vocabulary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.68,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies and gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.68,0:09:08.73,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Is it not boring to simply look at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:10.65,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this rhythm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.65,0:09:12.36,Main,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,It's making my heart dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.62,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to my new single,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:24.95,Main,Brook,0000,0000,0000,,"Bone to be Wild!"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.81,0:09:35.55,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,This is the underside of the giant bridge in East Blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.40,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,What brought about this change of attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:44.44,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,We are really grateful that you are coming with us to Baltigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:48.10,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,Dragon-san has always wanted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.72,0:09:54.05,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,If I had known you were such charitable people,\NI would have wanted you to come and see me sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.05,0:09:59.62,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're sorry!  We hadn't heard about your team-up with Crocodile.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:04.20,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke.  I was just teasing you.\NSorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:07.27,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad things turned out the way they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.21,0:10:12.59,Main,Voice,0000,0000,0000,,Set sail!  Set sail for Baltigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.52,0:10:42.63,Flashbacks,Saul,0000,0000,0000,,Go meet your true friends!  I'm sure they're waiting\Nout on the sea somewhere, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:47.00,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,Seventy-nine million Beli?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.42,0:10:50.29,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,An eight-year-old with a bounty that high?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.29,0:10:55.50,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,She's apparently a survivor from the demons of Ohara,\Nwho were plotting to destroy the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:57.45,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,From Ohara?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:01.84,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,And I have no idea how it happened, but she's supposed to have sunk six Navy warships as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.34,0:11:04.18,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why she got this insane bounty?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.15,0:11:09.97,Flashbacks,Dudey McMan,0000,0000,0000,,She is the child of demons,\Nand she mustn't be allowed to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.63,0:11:14.66,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, you just wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:21.74,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to save me?!\NWhen did I ever ask you to do that?!{This first half of this line is a copy-paste from 405. The second sentence is not.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.16,0:11:30.60,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to die! {Copy-paste from 405.}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:36.06,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I know exactly who Robin's enemy is. {Copy-paste from 431}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:40.09,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot down that flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:49.52,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible! {End copy-paste from 431}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.77,0:11:51.31,Flashbacks,Spandam,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys out of your minds?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.81,Flashbacks,Spandam,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you'll be able to survive with the entire world as your enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:59.93,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.49,0:12:04.16,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.70,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't heard it from your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.70,0:12:14.21,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Say that you want to live!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:25.93,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,If I really am allowed to express my true desires, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:28.89,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.94,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna live!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.06,0:12:38.77,Flashbacks,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me go out to sea with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:47.96,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,Robin-san, please come inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.96,0:12:49.58,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,It's cold out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:51.65,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be fine out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.65,0:12:55.27,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pirate.  You are revolutionaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.27,0:12:57.30,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:01.76,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I will not enter a cabin where there are no escape-routes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:05.68,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,What?!  We have no intention of harming you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.68,0:13:10.51,Main,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me stay.  Back when I was on my own,\Nthis was how I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:13.35,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:16.13,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Bring as many warm blankets as you can find!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.13,0:13:18.78,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,And something hot to drink and eat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.78,0:13:21.03,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,B-But we've got all that prepared inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.03,0:13:24.05,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!  And a wind guard and a sofa, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:24.90,Main,Revolutionary,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.00,0:13:28.01,Thoughts,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:33.21,Thoughts,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,If I go to your father,\Nand let the tides of the world direct me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.21,0:13:36.00,Thoughts,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I can become a little stronger?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.20,0:13:41.21,Thoughts,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to become stronger for the sake of someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:44.30,Thoughts,Robin,0000,0000,0000,,I'd never considered it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.09,0:13:52.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Visit us at http://www.yibis.com/
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:59.52,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Chat us up at #yibis@irc.rizon.net
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:05.20,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the Boyn Islands on the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:10.87,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,What is it now'n, Usopp'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.87,0:14:13.86,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I'll burn some fat!  And work out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:16.13,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Oh'n!  That's a great idea'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:17.87,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:21.21,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Good'n!  You can't get off the island otherwise'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.21,0:14:23.87,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll become even stronger than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.87,0:14:25.68,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Yes'n!  That sounds good too'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:29.25,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll become much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.25,0:14:30.50,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,That much'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.50,0:14:33.88,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Much, much, much, much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.88,0:14:35.85,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,You're incredibly motivated'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:39.53,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly starting to work out like that'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.77,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly was written in that paper'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:52.24,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I... received a message from our captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.70,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Message?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:57.78,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talking about?  Get onboard, already. {Oh just guess what episode THIS is a copy-paste from.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.37,0:15:02.96,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends, aren't we? {End of oh just guess what episode THIS is a copy-paste from.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.16,Flashbacks,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.12,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,U-Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.55,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.55,0:15:24.40,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,were here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:29.40,Flashbacks,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Win!  And then we'll all go back together, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.40,0:15:31.36,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we will!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:36.12,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:43.55,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,thought that Luffy could become the Pirate King on his own, I'd just stand by and watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.82,0:15:46.96,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,We've finally made it this far! {Copy-paste from 385}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.30,0:15:53.53,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,When we've crossed the other half of the world, and see this wall again...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.53,0:15:54.43,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.84,0:15:56.97,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the Pirate King! {End copy-paste from 385.}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.20,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,But I was wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.20,0:16:03.16,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Even he has plenty of enemies he can't beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.98,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Even Luffy can be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:09.61,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,He's pushing himself too hard!  He was screaming! { def: screaming? literal or metaphore?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:10.74,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.18,0:16:14.41,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}he needs my strength!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.07,0:16:20.74,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Heracles'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:22.66,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.66,0:16:25.58,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Much, much, much stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:31.13,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Heracles'n-sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:33.80,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?  Sensei'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:37.60,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I've been curious about those weapons of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:42.81,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,There's so much I want to learn from you, the man who survives on this island using his {\i1}amazing skills!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.81,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing skills'n?\NI am a sensei with amazing skills'n?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.69,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!  You are an amazingly skilled sensei! {To the editors/QC-arz: Please rework "Amazingly skilled" into something better-sounding}{ def: no! you translated it, now you live with it! well, unless someone else comes up with something better }
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.69,0:16:49.79,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,And,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.79,0:16:51.06,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,my name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:53.32,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Heracles'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.32,0:16:55.49,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,That's such a cool name!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.27,0:16:59.53,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!  Take a seat, Usopp'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.53,0:17:01.18,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:03.83,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, my student Usopp'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.67,0:17:12.42,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,There are plants on this island called Pop Green.  They are hostile and can sprout instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:16.64,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,These are their seeds'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.91,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Pop Green?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:23.52,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,They all have their uses'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.52,0:17:25.21,Main,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I see'n.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:27.38,Thoughts,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.70,0:17:33.86,Main,Heracles,0000,0000,0000,,Run, Usopp'n!  This forest will make you stronger'n!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.73,0:17:36.50,Thoughts,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,In order to help you become the Pirate King,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.23,0:17:40.91,Thoughts,Usopp,0000,0000,0000,,I will become a true King of Snipers!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:53.95,Narrator TOP,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And now, to Kuraigana Island on the Grand Line,\Nruins of Shikkearu Kingdom. {I would just like to point out that I am really looking forward to the time when the Straw Hats are back together and I won't have to write lines like THESE every single goddamn episode.}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:55.84,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:05.89,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Please, train me in the ways of the sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:09.01,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,I've misjudged you, Roronoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.97,0:18:14.03,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,You ask your sworn enemy to teach you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:15.80,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,You should be ashamed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:20.99,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of my sight.\NI have no business with such a worthless man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.41,0:18:24.98,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I overestimated you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:30.58,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?\NYou are only embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.52,0:18:33.50,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:36.86,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,You failed to defeat the baboons, and couldn't go out to sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:42.01,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,Then you crawled back here.\NI have nothing to teach one such as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.55,0:18:46.93,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I did defeat the baboons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.73,Thoughts,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,He beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.11,0:18:53.73,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I just need to take your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:19:00.11,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not so stupid to think I can beat you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.11,0:19:04.94,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,I do not understand.\NIf you still consider me your enemy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.94,0:19:08.12,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,why do you bow down before me\Nand ask me to train you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:10.35,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,For what purpose?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.02,0:19:14.00,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,So that I can surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.94,0:19:26.64,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,So you want me to personally train a swordsman who wants take my own head?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.07,0:19:30.58,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange fellow.  How ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:33.61,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,And you are still disgracing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.61,0:19:38.15,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem I have found a man\Ntruly filled with ambition.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:43.70,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, ghost-girl.  Tend to his wounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:47.08,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  Don't tell me what to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.06,0:19:50.27,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,The training will begin after your wounds have healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:55.35,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!  Everyone keeps ordering me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:57.74,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, get back to your room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:01.47,Thoughts,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,What an awkward man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:08.47,Thoughts,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,When someone like him discards his pride, it must be for the sake of another.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.60,0:20:13.10,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,"3D" with an X over it, and "2Y"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.10,0:20:16.27,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!  It's tattooed into Straw Hat's right arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.27,0:20:21.61,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,We made a promise to meet at a certain place\Nin three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.36,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,And now look at how it's turned out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.92,0:20:28.53,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,So "3D" stands for "Three days"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.53,0:20:32.10,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,But the "3D" is crossed out, and the "2Y" means...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.80,0:20:33.60,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.60,0:20:34.79,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Two years?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.79,0:20:38.96,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,We won't be meeting up in three days,\Nbut in two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:43.15,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Everything else was just a distraction\Nto hide the real message from everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.15,0:20:49.59,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,This message was meant only for us.  It's the decision that Luffy made.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.35,0:20:54.31,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,There's no point in rushing.\NAs we are, we won't stand a chance in the New World.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.31,0:20:56.75,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,We'll stop here, and increase our strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.73,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,And then we'll set sail once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.87,0:21:10.83,Main,Perona,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!  I'm telling you to go back to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.03,0:21:23.84,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.26,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,That won't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:32.72,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You... Just who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:35.70,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.40,0:21:38.69,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,The man who will become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.70,0:21:43.85,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Until the day I beat him and become the greatest swordsman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.82,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I swear I will not lose, ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.67,0:21:49.03,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,You got a problem with that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.75,Flashbacks,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Pirate King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.39,0:21:56.25,Flashbacks,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.57,0:22:00.26,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much time we have,\Nit won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.71,0:22:01.91,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Please begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.49,0:22:08.64,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,You said you defeated the baboons, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:13.01,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,The baboons who have learned\Nvarious sword techniques by mimicking humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.65,0:22:17.48,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,Of course there are ranks among them, and a master.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.86,0:22:21.30,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,You could call him the baboon king,\Nhe rules over all the baboons on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.80,0:22:25.78,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,That sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:29.34,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,He's mimicking me,\Nand attempting to improve his swordplay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.45,Main,Mihawk,0000,0000,0000,,He's on an entirely different level\Nfrom the baboons you've faced so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:33.86,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.58,0:22:37.47,Main,Zoro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep on getting stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.32,0:23:00.98,Main,Straw Hat Pirates,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We'll meet up in two years, at Sabaody Archipelago!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.45,0:23:13.30,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hat Pirates have decided to improve their skills before they regroup in two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:16.83,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy lands on the uninhabited island of Ruskaina.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.19,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,And, in order to meet the new adversaries and adventures waiting for him in the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.19,0:23:24.18,Narrator,Narrator,0000,0000,0000,,he begins training to use a new power!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.18,0:23:25.42,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.42,0:23:26.98,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's Training Begins
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.79,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,Meet in Two Years, at the Promised Place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.17,0:23:31.33,Main,Luffy,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!
